						               													<description>Into The Ashes is a dark solitaire adventure with tactical tabletop combat. It offers you a narrative campaign with dozens of hours and totally replayable. Its setup and saving take less than 1 second, and you can play as long as you want: from 5 minutes to all day. It will provide you with an epic story with hundreds of enemies, character evolution, legendary item crafting, and spectacular combos with cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn, the player chooses 3 cards to play from the matrix of available cards (initially 3x3 and, later, 4x3 and 5x3). The cards used contain actions such as &amp;quot;Attack&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Move&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Ranged Attack&amp;quot; or &amp;quot;Push&amp;quot;. The rule is that you cannot use, in a given turn, cards that repeat a row or column already chosen in that turn. Unused cards are available for the next turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With these cards, the player moves and performs actions on the board. The enemies, on the other hand, play their AI cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is a campaign of more than 10h of duration and ends when the campaign finishes. At any time you can stop and &amp;quot;save the game&amp;quot; to continue at another time. If the player is defeated in any scene, he does not die but is defeated and things will happen accordingly in the story.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player wins if he/she manages to reach one of the &amp;quot;good endings&amp;quot; of the campaign. There are other &amp;quot;bad endings&amp;quot; and other &amp;quot;neutral endings&amp;quot;, depending on the decisions made.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
